<section class="ak-module" data-module="resources" aria-label="Resources">

  <div class="eyebrow">OIATC · Resources · Sagamok Anishnawbek</div>
  <h1 class="display">Sagamok member resources</h1>
  <p class="lede">Ahnii. A plain-language guide to getting things done with the band, the programs you can use, and how Council works. Tap a question to see where to go.</p>
  <p class="r-note">A community resource put together by Russell Jones, a Sagamok Anishnawbek member, on behalf of OIATC. Independent of Sagamok Chief and Council and its administration. Everything links to an official Sagamok source. Contacts change over time; the <a href="https://www.sagamokanishnawbek.com/directory" target="_blank" rel="noopener">staff directory</a> is always the most current. Corrections welcome.</p>

