    <p style="margin:0; color:var(--ink); font-size:15px; max-width:62ch">The treaty-wide and community transparency work that members lead now has its own independent home, the Robinson Huron Treaty Members' Transparency Circle. It is independent of OIATC.</p>
    <a class="btn btn--primary" href="https://rhtcircle.ca" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit the Transparency Circle &rarr;</a>
  </div>

