      <div class="r-card" data-text="land hunting fishing environment lands resources lre keysis">
        <button type="button"><span>Ask about land, hunting, fishing, or the environment</span><span class="r-chev">&#8250;</span></button>
        <div class="r-body">
          <p>Lands, Resources and Environment handles land, harvesting, and environmental matters.</p>
          <div class="r-who">
            <span class="r-pill"><b>Lands, Resources &amp; Environment</b> (705) 863-0494</span>
