          <div class="r-who">
            <span class="r-pill"><b>Community Justice</b> (705) 865-1884</span>
            <span class="r-pill"><b>Anishinabek Police</b> 1-888-310-1122</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="r-card" data-text="elder elders long term care eagle lodge seniors">
        <button type="button"><span>Reach Elder care or long-term care</span><span class="r-chev">&#8250;</span></button>
        <div class="r-body">
          <p>Long-term care and Elder support run through the Elders Eagle Lodge.</p>
          <div class="r-who">
            <span class="r-pill"><b>Elders Eagle Lodge</b> (705) 865-2926</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="r-card" data-text="council chief bring something agenda secretariat political office meeting toulouse">
        <button type="button"><span>Bring something to Chief and Council</span><span class="r-chev">&#8250;</span></button>
        <div class="r-body">
